<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Curves on Chen Kai Blog</title><link>https://www.chenk.top/zh/tags/curves/</link><description>Recent content in Curves on Chen Kai Blog</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 01 May 2021 09:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.chenk.top/zh/tags/curves/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>微分几何（一）：空间曲线——曲率、挠率与 Frenet 标架</title><link>https://www.chenk.top/zh/differential-geometry/01-%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E6%9B%B2%E7%BA%BF/</link><pubDate>Sat, 01 May 2021 09:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.chenk.top/zh/differential-geometry/01-%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E6%9B%B2%E7%BA%BF/</guid><description>&lt;p>一条曲线是微分几何中最简单的对象——一维的东西，住在三维空间里。但即便这么简单，数学已经足够丰富。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="参数化曲线" class="heading-anchor">参数化曲线&lt;a href="#%e5%8f%82%e6%95%b0%e5%8c%96%e6%9b%b2%e7%ba%bf" class="heading-link" aria-label="Permalink to this section" title="Copy link to this section">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>&lt;span class="math-inline">$\mathbb{R}^3$&lt;/span>
 中一条光滑曲线就是一个映射 &lt;span class="math-inline">$\alpha: I \to \mathbb{R}^3$&lt;/span>
，其中 &lt;span class="math-inline">$I$&lt;/span>
 是开区间，&lt;span class="math-inline">$\alpha$&lt;/span>
 无穷次可微。速度向量 &lt;span class="math-inline">$\alpha&amp;#39;(t)$&lt;/span>
 不为零时，称曲线&lt;strong>正则&lt;/strong>——没有尖点，没有停顿。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>